    "split_image_text_cRMdBV": {
      "type": "splitImageText",
      "blocks": {
        "block_iyYi76": {
          "type": "block",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify:\/\/shop_images\/DCR03249.jpg",
            "heading": "CONTRACT MANUFACTURING CAPABILITIES",
            "subheading": "",
            "content": "<p>Our contract manufacturing capabilities support high-volume confectionery programs for national retailers, specialty brands, and private label partners. With advanced chocolate panning systems, automated production lines, and dedicated quality assurance processes, Sconza delivers consistent, scalable manufacturing for confectionery brands to grow.<br\/><\/p><ul><li>Chocolate, sugar, and specialty panning systems<\/li><li>High-capacity roasting and hot panning<\/li><li>Mogul and deposited confection lines<\/li><li>Nuts, dried & freeze-dried fruits and caramels<\/li><li>On-site liquid chocolate system for continuous production<\/li><\/ul>",
            "button_text": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "block_gwYHUJ": {
          "type": "block",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify:\/\/shop_images\/DSC_1325-si.jpg",
            "heading": "Scalable Confectionery Manufacturing",
            "subheading": "",
            "content": "<p>Our confectionery manufacturing infrastructure is designed to support high-volume production for national retail and private label programs. From initial product launch to large-scale retail distribution, Sconza provides the capacity, quality systems, and operational flexibility required by leading brands.<\/p><ul><li>Multi-shift, high-volume capacity<\/li><li>Seasonal program execution<\/li><li>Retail, club, and specialty channel expertise<\/li><li>Toll to turnkey manufacturing models<\/li><li>National and international distribution support<\/li><\/ul>",
            "button_text": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "alignment": "left"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "block_iyYi76",
        "block_gwYHUJ"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "heading": "",
        "subheading": "",
        "content": "",
        "button_text": "",
        "button_link": "",
        "alignment": "center"
      }
    },
    "split_image_text_Fa4Y8b": {
      "type": "splitImageText",
      "blocks": {
        "block_UpJmie": {
          "type": "block",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify:\/\/shop_images\/SconzaAerial-001.jpg",
            "heading": "Contract Manufacturing",
            "subheading": "Custom Confectionery Solutions at Scale",
            "content": "<p><strong>High-Volume Capacity<\/strong><\/p><p>Our 500,000 square-foot facility is filled with state -of-the-art equipment, including two rail spurs and 1.8 MM pounds of liquid chocolate<br\/>storage.<\/p><p><strong>Fast Turnaround Times<\/strong><\/p><p>With 200 employees working around the clock, we make sure your orders are filled quickly and with expert care.<\/p><p><strong>One-Stop Shop<\/strong><\/p><p>From <strong>chocolate panning<\/strong> and <strong>sugar panning<\/strong> to a wide range of confection formats, we support your program from concept to finished product—helping you get more candy into customers’ hands, faster.<br\/><br\/><\/p>",
            "button_text": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "block_eYKGWf": {
          "type": "block",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify:\/\/shop_images\/FactoryFloor-002.jpg",
            "heading": "Confectionary Capabilities",
            "subheading": "Private Label",
            "content": "<p><strong>Chocolate & Sugar Panned Confections<\/strong><br\/>Layered coatings, premium finishes, scalable production.<\/p><p><strong>Chocolate-Coated Fruits, Nuts & Centers<\/strong><br\/>Almonds, berries, crisped centers, and specialty inclusions.<\/p><p><strong>Seasonal & Everyday Programs<\/strong><br\/>Holiday assortments, limited-time launches, and evergreen favorites.<\/p><p><strong>Custom Formats <\/strong><br\/>Flavor development, format innovation, and retail-ready production.<\/p>",
            "button_text": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "alignment": "left"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "block_UpJmie",
        "block_eYKGWf"
